Ad Description: The HTML5 Responsive Rich Media Banner is a rich banner that is able to resize responsively or adaptively to fill the available space. There are multiple templates available, demonstrating multiple ways to create designs that can adapt to a variety of dimensions. The format also supports using one fixed size for ad placements that do not change size.



