HTML5 Responsive Billboard
















HTML5 Responsive Billboard




                save to my galleries
            


Demo
			  

Build Guides
			

Download
			







Ad Description: The HTML5 Responsive Billboard format can be used for creating a responsive billboard effect on a publisher’s page.  This format has two different states: the expanded or banner state (Billboard) and the collapsed/unexpanded state (Leave Behind). The billboard can adjust to different breakpoints, either animating responsively between breakpoints as the ad is resized, or snapping between breakpoints without a transitional animation (using the mdSnapPointAnimation variable). 


Demo
			  

Build Guides
			

Download
			






















