Liquid


Responsive Expandable
















Responsive Expandable




                save to my galleries
            


Demo
			  

Build Guides
			

Download
			







Ad Description: The Responsive Expandable is an expandable format that is able to resize responsively or adaptively to fill the available space. Different rules for responsive behavior can be separately customized for the banner and the panels. The format also supports using fixed sizes for ad placements that do not change size.

For example, you can now set the banner to responsive to the advertiser container so that the unit resizes as the advertiser div resizes, or you can even appear full width and fixed height in the browser for a hero-style banner. The panel has many customizations available, such as adaptive scaling, matching the banner for dimensions as you resize, or scaling by aspect ratio. You can also turn the expanded panel into a fullscreen unit for the width and height, by customizing it to expand to those dimensions.


Demo
			  

Build Guides
			

Download
			






















Browser/OS Support SupportedNot Supported


BUILD
Desktop
Tablet
Mobile




