Ad Description: The Billboard is a top-performing IAB Rising Star format that appears initially as a 970x250 banner and contains a prominent “close ad” button in the top right corner. If a user clicks the button, the ad will collapse into a tiny banner in the top right corner, and the publisher page content will shift up to fill in the space. This format includes images, videos, user actions and click-through buttons, but it can be customized with interactive features ranging from games to face recognition. Some publishers permit a companion banner or a drag feature that can reveal additional content.


