Pushdown
















Pushdown




                save to my galleries
            


Demo
			  


Build Guides
					


HTML5 Pushdown Banner (Single Panel)
HTML5 Pushdown (Multi Panel, Workspace)
HTML5 Pushdown (Multi Panel, Ad Builder)




Downloads
					


HTML5 Pushdown Banner (Single Panel) 1.1.0
HTML5 Pushdown (Multi Panel) 2.1.0









Ad Description: Note: For the HTML5 Versions of this format, you must select "HTML5 Pushdown Banner" format on the platform when using the Single Expandable version of Pushdown and you must select "HTML5 Pushdown" format on the platform when using the Expandable Banner version.  You MUST be careful not to mix up these two formats when setting up your HTML5 ads.

The Pushdown format pushes site content down as the ad expands, allowing the user to still see site content after expansion. The ad loads in the collapsed state, then the ad can either be expanded or clicked through to another site by tapping the buttons. From the expanded state, the user may either click the UserAction button or close the ad and return to the collapsed state. Clicking the UserAction button sends a custom interaction and is tracked in reports. Some Pushdown templates contain a video player, which is set up to track video interactions.


Demo
			  


Build Guides
					


HTML5 Pushdown Banner (Single Panel)
HTML5 Pushdown (Multi Panel, Workspace)
HTML5 Pushdown (Multi Panel, Ad Builder)




Downloads
					


HTML5 Pushdown Banner (Single Panel) 1.1.0
HTML5 Pushdown (Multi Panel) 2.1.0
























