Pandora Responsive Banner















Pandora Responsive Banner




                save to my galleries
            


Build Guides
			

Download
			







Ad Description: The Pandora Responsive Banner is a responsive format that dynamically chooses the ad’s banner size based on the available space within the Pandora app. Pandora supplies a square “L1” ad container that will be different sizes on different phones/tablets based not only on the device but the orientation of the device. The Pandora Responsive Banner will fill the “L1” ad container, but if a clickthrough is performed, the URL is opened up in the larger “L2” ad container space.


Build Guides
			

Download
			






















