Cascade
















Cascade




                save to my galleries
            


Demo
			  

Build Guides
			

Download
			







Ad Description: The Cascade format is initially 940x230 in size and allows for multiple panels of rich content. Up and down arrows allow the user to scroll through the available panels and display a cascade-like animation during navigation. Clicking the more button on any panel expands the unit to display the next panel in the series using a unique 3D flipbook-like animation (more button only displays if there is room in the viewport for expansion). The Cascade is a great way to present videos, image galleries, product carousels, social features, and more - then let the user decide which interests them the most.


