Workspace
Ad Builder



Download
			







Ad Description: The Out-stream Pushdown is a format that positions video advertisement content within the page content. This format launches when in view on the screen, activating only when readers scroll past them. Plays video when Ad is 50% visible in viewport area. Pause video once user scrolls the page and Ad goes out of viewport area. This format contains 1x1 and 400x40 templates.


