HTML5 VPAID Responsive















HTML5 VPAID Responsive




                save to my galleries
            


Demo
			  

Build Guides
		

Download
			







Ad Description: The HTML5 VPAID Responsive Template is designed to simplify to help you build interactive video experiences in an omni-screen world. HTML5 VPAID can be run across and a large variety of screen sizes – from full-screen desktop, to inline video within a mobile device. It’s important to make sure that the integrity of the interactive experience is preserved across a variety of screen sizes. The HTML5 VPAID Responsive Template provides the necessary elements that allow you to manage and control responsive behavior of individual assets and overlays within your interactive video ad with ease.


Demo
			  

Build Guides
		

Download
			























