Liquid


Full-Screen Expandable
















Full-Screen Expandable




                save to my galleries
            


Demo
			  


Build Guides
					


HTML5
Ad Builder



Download
			







Ad Description: The “HTML5 Full-Screen Expandable” format contains a call to action to expand the ad over the page content. The ad loads with banner on page with expand button, clicking expand button expands the ad to full size of the screen on a mobile device or to the full size of the browser window on a desktop. On mobile devices the expansion will even dynamically resize as the orientation changes (e.g. portrait or landscape) or dynamically resize as a desktop browser is resized. This format allows one tag to be served across different domains where Certification and Support can use the “Domain Configuration Tool” to change custom variables, JavaScript and CSS on specific domains so a single tag can work everywhere as expected, which means different custom variable settings can be used across different sites and site sections.Note: A similar format that was based on the Single Expandable called “HTML5 Full Screen Expandable Banner” has been deprecated and all users should be creating their full screen expandable ads with this format going forward


Demo
			  


